            <div class="title">
                Tribunals Of Inquiry (Evidence) Act, 1921
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-06-12/debates/44e45587-3e3b-4ecb-9e1d-844beec86aa9/CivilDefenceBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
